name: Smuggler's Warning About Sister Alitura
description: Good news from Kirus. Remember that Sisters of EVE agent, Alitura, who nearly caught our trail? The boss called in some favors and got her reassigned to Arnon IX in Essence. The good Sister Alitura may be resourceful, but she'd need a capsuleer with clearance to all four empires to be any threat, and we know how much the Sisters love capsuleers.
